Also as a huge fan of League of Legends Esports, this website also have some data visualizations using the data set of Pro-League all around the world in season 12 of this game. Like all other sports, this game have a huge amount of audience all around the world, this sports has a trending development over the past few years. And as the Mid-Season Invitational of Season 13 has just began, more and more fans would like to get deeper into this game and this website will help with understanding League of Legends Esports by looking through and gathering the data of past season, season 12, mainly foucsing on champions. Go through the drop down links on the top right corner called $LOL$ $Eports$ to get more informations.
